title: Windows Server 2008 R2 SP1 x64 Vanilla
description:
I was sick and tired of looking for an unmodded Server 2008 R2 SP1 ISO, so I
set out on a journey to find one, which led me to an unsecured Brazilian webserver running "Http File Server" (for those of you who do not know what that is, it is a free, REALLY simple free http server for windows) and spent 7 hours downloading it xD

Hope you enjoy!
